生，該區嘅國會議員都代表你。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋效法G20攬炒團隊的視野，大家為咗香港為咗公義，需要行前多一步接觸身邊嘅人，將香港議題推向世界，要讓議員看到這法案在美國普羅大眾有認受性。萬事起頭難，但我哋對大家有信心。香港人加油!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係簡單製作印刷說明:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Step 1</span>: pdf files to print: (DON&rsquo;T USE THE PNG FILES, USE THESE)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WQ2jKehPE-89sfH91nyFuThJujf5tSWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1WQ2jKehPE-89sfH91nyFuThJujf5tSWE&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDagSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=91bc30ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WQ2jKehPE-89sfH91nyFuThJujf5tSWE</a><br />\n<br />\nTry printing on 100lbs cardstock, which is standard for postcard.  Most printing companies can print 500 in two days.  Could use 120lbs for a more sturdy touch. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Step 2</span>: ask each person supporting HKHRDA to write their name and return address at the top left corner.  This will show the member of congress our support of the Act is not some robo-call or spam.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Step 3</span>: write &ldquo;The Honorable&rdquo; before the name of the Senator/Representative and then write their local office address. Mail a postcard to each of the following:<br />\n  &mdash; two Senators of their state, <br />\n  &mdash; the House of Representative of their congressional district<br />\n(look up your member of congress at <a href=\"https://www.govtrack.us/congress/members\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtrack.us%2Fcongress%2Fmembers&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDagSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=b282d098\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtrack.us/congress/members</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Step 4</span> (optional, for booth or rally): pre-print address labels of Senators and Representatives&rsquo; office of your state:<br />\n<br />\n1. Purchase any brand name address labels that fit 30 labels per 8.5&rdquo;x11&rdquo; US letter size paper<br />\n<br />\n2. Open Microsoft Word:<br />\n<br />\n3. Go to <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Mailings</span></strong> &gt; <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Labels</span></strong>.<br />\n<br />\n4. Select<strong> <span style=\"color: red;\">Options</span></strong> and choose a &ldquo;Microsoft&rdquo; as Label vendors. <br />\n<br />\n5. Scroll down at the Product number menu, select second &ldquo;30 Per Page&rdquo;.  Dimension should be Height 1&rdquo; and Width 2.63&rdquo;.  Select <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">OK</span></strong>.<br />\n<br />\n6. At Address: put in &ldquo;The Honorable&rdquo; before the name of the senator/representative and then put in their local office address. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山<br />\n各自努力<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:57:08.000Z","msg":"&quot;as a proud citizen of the United States...&quot;<br />\n可唔可以出一個非公民Ver. 改做<br />\n&quot;as a proud resident of the United States...&quot;"},{"pid":"db1b5b0796a23002f6edbc6e492139d7296e59ff","tid":1610999,"uid":168104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:57:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0c17701d4abc61865bca1293953a025c7affc7e6","tid":1610999,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:58:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2250471def38c45f4bcc79f82c4f23e29536e29","tid":1610999,"uid":303794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"即做！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ff465808aad862db3bea3de555f8d76084ce6c","tid":1610999,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b58248f34e43